OL,3,CWhat is stalking and who can help you?
OL,4,CHow to recognise the signs
OL,6,FSometimes it is really ordinary
OL,7,Fbehaviours like repeated text
OL,8,Fmessages, phone calls, emails. It
OL,9,Fcould be making malicious complaints
OL,10,Fabout somebody, it could be giving
OL,11,Fgifts, it could be monitoring someone
OL,12,Fcovertly.
OL,14,FMost police and charities use the
OL,15,Fmnemonic FOUR to define stalking:
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/17
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
