OL,3,CWhat is stalking and who can help you?
OL,4,CHow to recognise the signs
OL,6,FJane Harvey, CEO of the Hollie Gazzard
OL,7,FTrust, said: "The advice I'd give is
OL,8,Fthat if someone's behaviour towards
OL,9,Fyou is making you feel uncomfortable
OL,10,Ftake notice of that, trust your
OL,11,Finstinct.
OL,13,F"That's how stalking starts, it starts
OL,14,Fso subtly and it starts with someone
OL,15,Ffeeling uncomfortable, awkward, just a
OL,16,Flittle voice in your head or feeling
OL,17,Fin your gut that something isn't quite
OL,18,Fright.
OL,26,@oD@NOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/17
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
