OL,3,CWhat is stalking and who can help you?
OL,4,CHow to recognise the signs
OL,6,F"Maybe that comes to nothing but it's
OL,7,Freally important that you take notice
OL,8,Fof that."
OL,10,FWhat is cyber stalking?
OL,12,FCyber stalking is stalking conducted
OL,13,Fthrough the online sphere and/or
OL,14,Ftechnology.
OL,16,FLike any type of stalking, it can take
OL,17,Fmany different forms - from receiving
OL,18,Fpersistent messages to realising
OL,19,Fsomeone has created a fake account
OL,20,Fpretending to be you.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@IO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/17
