OL,3,CWhat is stalking and who can help you?
OL,4,CHow to recognise the signs
OL,6,FIt could include someone putting a
OL,7,Ftracking device onto your car or using
OL,8,Fyour phone to track you.
OL,10,FAs well as hacking into your social
OL,11,Fmedia accounts to find out what you're
OL,12,Fdoing or using home technology - such
OL,13,Fas smart lights - against you.
OL,15,FMegan Haldane, a Cyber Protect Officer
OL,16,Fat Avon and Somerset Police said:
OL,17,F"Classically, if you pictured stalking
OL,18,Fseveral years ago it was following
OL,19,Fsomeone down a street in its most
OL,20,Fclassic format.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/17
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
