OL,3,CWhat is stalking and who can help you?
OL,4,CHow to recognise the signs
OL,6,FStalking can impact anyone. According
OL,7,Fto figures compiled by the ONS in the
OL,8,Fyear up to March 2025, more than 1.4
OL,9,Fmillion people reported being victims
OL,10,Fof stalking in the UK.
OL,12,FMore than 6.7 million people say they
OL,13,Fhave experienced staking since the age
OL,14,Fof 16.
OL,16,FThat is 1 in 5 women in the UK and 1
OL,17,Fin 11 men who have experienced
OL,18,Fstalking.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/17
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
