OL,3,CWhat is stalking and who can help you?
OL,4,CHow to recognise the signs
OL,6,FData compiled by the ONS shows the
OL,7,Fpercentage of people aged 16 years and
OL,8,Fover who were victims of stalking in
OL,9,Fthe last year, by personal
OL,10,Fcharacteristics:
OL,12,FAre some people more at risk of
OL,13,Fstalking than others?
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/17
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
