OL,3,CWhat is stalking and who can help you?
OL,4,CHow to recognise the signs
OL,6,FWhat should you do if you think
OL,7,Fsomeone you know is being stalked?
OL,9,FIf somebody tells you that they're
OL,10,Fgetting unwanted contact from someone
OL,11,F- you should listen to them. Charities
OL,12,Fsuggest that you can help them keep a
OL,13,Fdiary of what is happening, when,
OL,14,Fwhere and how it made them feel. You
OL,15,Fcan also point them in the direction
OL,16,Fof professional help either through
OL,17,Fthe police or other support services.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/17
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
