OL,3,CWhat is stalking and who can help you?
OL,4,CHow to recognise the signs
OL,6,FYou can also use Clare's Law to
OL,7,Finquire with your local police force
OL,8,Fabout a current or ex-partner's
OL,9,Fabusive history. You can make an
OL,10,Fapplication on behalf of someone else
OL,11,Fif you are worried about them.
OL,13,FWhat is Clare's Law?
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/17
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
