OL,3,CWhat is stalking and who can help you?
OL,4,CHow to recognise the signs
OL,6,FNamed after Clare Wood, who was killed
OL,7,Fby her abusive ex-partner in 2009, the
OL,8,Finitiative allows the public to
OL,9,Frequest police information if there
OL,10,Fare concerns over someone's history of
OL,11,Fabuse and they are a risk to you. A
OL,12,Ffriend or relative can also apply for
OL,13,Finformation.
OL,15,FThe Domestic Violence Disclosure
OL,16,FScheme is in place to help protect
OL,17,Fpeople at risk and prevent further
OL,18,Fcrimes.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/17
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
