OL,3,CWhat is stalking and who can help you?
OL,4,CHow to recognise the signs
OL,6,F"During my career I have spoken to a
OL,7,Fnumber of parents whose daughters have
OL,8,Fbeen killed and they have told me they
OL,9,Fdidn't take it seriously and later
OL,10,Fwell they've spent the rest of their
OL,11,Flives regretting not taking it
OL,12,Fseriously."
OL,14,FHow do I tell the police?
OL,16,FIf you feel you are in immediate
OL,17,Fdanger you should call 999. If at the
OL,18,Fpoint you decide to report you feel
OL,19,Freasonably safe you can call 111 or
OL,20,Fyou can report to the police online.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@KO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/17
